Individual




Peter G. Leemputte



Mr. Peter G. Leemputte is Chief Financial Officer & Treasurer at Keurig Green Mountain, Inc., Independent Director at Beazer Homes USA, Inc., and a Member-National Council at Washington University School of Engineering & Applied Sci. He is on the Board of Directors at Beazer Homes USA, Inc.
Mr. Leemputte was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Mead Johnson Nutrition Co., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Brunswick Corp., Controller & Head-Operations Analysis by FMC Corp., EVP, Chief Financial & Administrative Officer by Chicago Title Corp., a Principal by BP Amoco Corp., Product Development Engineer by Procter & Gamble Co., Vice President by Mercer Management Consulting, Inc., and Vice President & Controller by Armco, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Washington University in St. Louis and an MBA from The University of Chicago Booth School of Business.



